That he the volume much esteem'd;

line_1: By all mankind a prodigy esteem'd?

line_1: For virtue honour'd, and for parts esteem'd;

line_2: When to my Swain reserv'd I seem'd,

line_1: In public by no man esteem'd,
So much is Scotland by the Queen esteem'd,
line_2: As Ships of the Built of Great-Britain deem'd:

line_1: Little themselves, their Passions less esteem'd.
